{"lemma":"رَدَى","slug":"رَدَى","root":"ر.د.#","root_slug":"ر-د-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-د-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15196","n15306","n15312","n15318"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of رَدِيَ (radiya) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of رَدِيَ (radiya) (form I); death, destruction","examples":[{"text":"يَا غُصْنَ نَقَا مُكَلَّلًا بِٱلذَّهَبِ – أَفْدِيكَ مِنَ ٱلرَّدَى بِأُمِّي وَأَبِي","english":"Oh branch of the sand dune wreathed in gold – I ransom you from death by my mother and my father"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cause the death of, to smite"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to annihilate, to raze","tags":["figuratively"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ra.dan/","/rad.daː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15196","headword_ar":"رُدَّى","root":"rd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maroduwdN","text_ar":"مَرْدُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n15306","headword_ar":"رَدِىَ","root":"rdY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarodaY","text_ar":"يَرْدَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radFY","text_ar":"رَدًى"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perished."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K.) [See an ex. in the Kur xx. 17.] ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radiYa","text_ar":"رَدِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, T, M, and so in a copy of the S,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarodaY","text_ar":"يَرْدَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, T,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radFY","text_ar":"رَدًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaY","text_ar":"رَدَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, and so in copies of the S;) or both of these verbs; aor. of the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarodiY","text_ar":"يَرْدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trd~Y","text_ar":"تردّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fell"},{"kind":"text","text":"into a well: (AZ, * T, * S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he tumbled down"},{"kind":"text","text":"into a deep hollow, or cavity, or pit: (M:) or ↓ the last of these verbs has this meaning: (Lth, T:) or it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he fell"},{"kind":"text","text":"into a deep hollow, or cavity, or pit: (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he tumbled down"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) from a mountain; (AZ, T, S;) and so the first, or second: (S:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trd~Y","text_ar":"تردّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he fell from a mountain and died."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA","text_ar":"اـِذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarad~aY","text_ar":"تَرَدَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xcii. 11], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When he falls into the abyss of the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of Hell"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (T, * TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into the cavity of the grave:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into the lowest depth of Hell:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he perishes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he dies."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaY","text_ar":"رَدَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^adoriY A^ayona radaY","text_ar":"مَا اَدْرِى اَيْنَ رَدَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I know not whither he went away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has gone away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaAhu","text_ar":"رَدَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarodiY","text_ar":"يَرْدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radoYN","text_ar":"رَدْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) namely, a thing with a stone: (M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he beat it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"battered it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] namely, a stone with a piece of rock, or with a pickaxe,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order to break it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He dashed himself against him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knocked against him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like as the pickaxe knocks against the stone."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaAhu biHajarK","text_ar":"رَدَاهُ بِحَجَرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biHijaArapK","text_ar":"بِحِجَارَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarodiY","text_ar":"يَرْدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radoYN","text_ar":"رَدْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaAhu biHajarK","text_ar":"رَدَاهُ بِحَجَرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rdw","text_ar":"ردو"},{"kind":"text","text":",) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaroduw","text_ar":"يَرْدُو"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radowN","text_ar":"رَدْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the final radical; (K, TA;) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaA^ahu","text_ar":"رَدَاَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraA^ahu","text_ar":"دَرَاَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":";]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threw at him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"threw at him and hit him, with a stone, or stones."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M.) [It is also said in the T, with reference to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mirodaApN","text_ar":"مِرْدَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as signifying a large stone with which other stones are beaten, or battered,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~adoYu A_in~amaA huwa rafoEN bihaA waramoYN bihaA","text_ar":"الرَّدْىُ اـِنَّمَا هُوَ رَفْعٌ بِهَا وَرَمْىٌ بِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but I think that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafoEN","text_ar":"رَفْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafoEN","text_ar":"دَفْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and that the meaning intended to be expressed by these words is, that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radoYN","text_ar":"رَدْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thrusting"},{"kind":"text","text":"with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mirodaAp","text_ar":"مِرْدَاة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throwing"},{"kind":"text","text":"it, or with it.] ―         -b4-  [Hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaY","text_ar":"رَدَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a horse, (As, ISk, T, S, M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarodiY","text_ar":"يَرْدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, ISk, T, S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radoYN","text_ar":"رَدْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radayaAnN","text_ar":"رَدَيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (ISk, S, M, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaA","text_ar":"رَدَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rdw","text_ar":"ردو"},{"kind":"text","text":", [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"is omitted before the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lugapN","text_ar":"لُغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in that art.,]) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaroduw","text_ar":"يَرْدُو"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [and, accord. to Freytag, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtdY","text_ar":"ارتدى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used in the same sense by Jereer;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He beat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"battered, the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajama","text_ar":"رَجَمَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroDa","text_ar":"الاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", As, ISk, T, S, ISk, T, S, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his hoofs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in running,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, T,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in going along,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in running,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in going a pace between running and vehement walking:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radayaAnN","text_ar":"رَدَيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoriybN","text_ar":"تَقْرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AZ, T, M: [see 2 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qrb","text_ar":"قرب"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or it is ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a manner of going"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between running and walking:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"running"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M) of the horse (T) or of the ass (S, M)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=riY~","text_ar":"ا=رِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of confinement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the loop to which he is tied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mutamaE~ak","text_ar":"مُتَمَعَّك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of rolling upon the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (T, S, M;) thus explained by El-Munteji' Ibn-Nebhán, (T, S,) to As. (S.) In the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajamato","text_ar":"رَجَمَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajama","text_ar":"رَجَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; being app. taken from the M, in which it refers to horses; [not to a single horse;] as does also the pronoun in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biHawaAfirihaA","text_ar":"بِحَوَافِرِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the same portion of the passage in the K and in the M. (TA.) Accord. to AZ, this is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radayaAnu AljawaAriY","text_ar":"رَدَيَانُ الجَوَارِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", explained"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in"},{"kind":"text","text":"what follows. (Ham p. 221.) ―         -b5-  You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radati AljaAriyapu","text_ar":"رَدَتِ الجَارِيَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The girl raised one leg and went along upon the other, in play;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Airotadat","text_ar":"اِرْتَدَت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljawaAriY yurodiyna","text_ar":"الجَوَارِى يُرْدِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radayaAnN","text_ar":"رَدَيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarotadiyna","text_ar":"يَرْتَدِينَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the girls played,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raising one leg,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of them raising one leg,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and going along upon the other:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radayaAnu AljawaAriY","text_ar":"رَدَيَانُ الجَوَارِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the girls' playing in which one of them raises one leg and steps with the other two steps, and then puts it down and raises the other, doing thus several times."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, Ham p. 221.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaY AlgulaAmu","text_ar":"رَدَى الغُلَامُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The boy raised one leg and leaped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"jumped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hopped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the other."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaY AlguraAbu","text_ar":"رَدَى الغُرَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarodiY","text_ar":"يَرْدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The crow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raven, raised one leg and hopped on the other;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaped along."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radato ganamiY","text_ar":"رَدَتْ غَنَمِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My sheep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats, increased,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exceeded;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arodato","text_ar":"اَرْدَتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Fr, M, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radayotu EalaY Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"رَدَيْتُ عَلَى الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ardyt","text_ar":"ارديت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I exceeded the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY gayorihi","text_ar":"عَلَى غَيْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArdY","text_ar":"اردى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It exceeded another thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArdA^","text_ar":"اردا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] (M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rdA^","text_ar":"ردا"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radayotu EalaY Alxamosiyna","text_ar":"رَدَيْتُ عَلَى الخَمْسِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, *) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alv~amaAniyna","text_ar":"الثَّمَانِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ardyt","text_ar":"ارديت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I exceeded"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"text","text":"age of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fifty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eighty"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, M. *)"}],"source_refs":["AZ","T","M","Lth","Msb","S","Bd","K","TK","TA","As","ISk"]},{"entry_id":"n15312","headword_ar":"رَدًى","root":"rdY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radiYa","text_ar":"رَدِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S, M, Msb, K.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Excess, redundance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"superfluity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ziyaAdapN","text_ar":"زِيَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA balagotu radaY EaTiy~atika","text_ar":"مَا بَلَغْتُ رَدَى عَطِيَّتِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not attained to thy excess,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in thy gift:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuEojibuniY radaY qawolika","text_ar":"يُعْجِبُنِى رَدَى قَوْلِكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The excess of thy saying pleases me:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so in the saying of Kutheiyir,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"lahu Eahodu wud~K lamo yakad~aro yaziynuhu\n                      \n                     \n                        radaY qawoli maEoruwfK HadiyvK wamuzomini"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has a covenant of love,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"into which he has entered,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which has not been sullied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which excess of kind speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"on his part, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recent and of long duration,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adorns:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or, [as ISd cites the verse,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawoli maEoruwfK","text_ar":"قَوْلِ مَعْرُوفٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radiY","text_ar":"رَدِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: [and he adds,] it is said, in explanation thereof, that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radiY","text_ar":"رَدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ziyaAdap","text_ar":"زِيَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and I think that it is an inf. n., of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEilN","text_ar":"فَعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaHikN","text_ar":"ضَحِكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabiqN","text_ar":"حَبِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or a subst. put in the place of an inf. n. (M.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radaApN","text_ar":"رَدَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["T"]},{"entry_id":"n15318","headword_ar":"رَدِىٌّ","root":"rdY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radiYo'N","text_ar":"رَدِىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rdA^","text_ar":"ردا"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}